## i18n-T1 Locale detection and switching
**Status:** implemented
**Type:** Unit
**Test File:** `frontend/src/i18n/index.ts`
**Module:** i18n
**Tags:** stack:frontend, module:i18n
**Depends on:** i18n-D1

### Cases

| ID | Description | Expected |
|----|-------------|----------|
| TC-T1.1 | `detectLocale()` returns stored locale | Stored value |
| TC-T1.2 | `detectLocale()` falls back to browser zh | `zh` |
| TC-T1.3 | `detectLocale()` falls back to `en` | `en` |
| TC-T1.4 | `setLocale()` updates i18n locale | Active locale changes |

